      "raw_text": "Our minimum SDK version is now high enough that all the currently required functions are available. And if we want to use more recently added functions in the future, we now support weak symbols. So the API wrapper is unnecessary.",
      "author": "jnicol@mozilla.com",
      "attachment_id": null,
      "time": "2026-01-21T09:15:43Z",
      "reactions": {},
      "id": 17852452,
      "is_private": false,
      "text": "Our minimum SDK version is now high enough that all the currently required functions are available. And if we want to use more recently added functions in the future, we now support weak symbols. So the API wrapper is unnecessary.",
      "count": 0,
      "tags": [],
